active_skill.name: Ether Bubble
active_skill.description:
Releases Ether bubbles that generate Energy for characters coming into contact with them.

Energy Generation: [3+Bangboo Level×0.05]/[3.1+Bangboo Level×0.05]/[3.2+Bangboo Level×0.05]/[3.3+Bangboo Level×0.05]/[3.4+Bangboo Level×0.05]

Cooldown 26s

additional_ability.name: Balanced Pressure
additional_ability.description: When there is at least one Support character in your squad: When Ether bubbles come into contact with characters, they additionally generate 60%/70%/80%/90%/100% of the original effect's Energy for off-field characters.
